      "comment": "SPRING QUIZ (1) was in the minors two back (22.23) at Ballarat but ran below best last time at Shepparton, finishing 6th. Has ability and can bounce back. HARD STYLE ROBBO (2) found the frame for the second consecutive time when narrowly beaten into second last time out (24.43) over 425m at this track. Can hit the frame this time. BLUE BOY SHIRAZ (7) turned in a better run last time to find a minor placing (22.45) at Shepparton behind I'm Honey in a Grade 5. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. The form out of the last run is proven to be strong. Leading player again. DIM SIM OLLIE (8) got up for a shock win last time and can go on with it.",
